Business Problem

Sales teams rely on Salesforce CRM to manage accounts, opportunities, and customer interactions. However, navigating multiple dashboards and records to retrieve insights or update information can be time-consuming and inefficient.

Sales representatives often need quick access to customer data, deal updates, and recommendations to close opportunities faster.

The business needs a solution that can:

⭐ Provide account insights quickly
⭐ Predict customer intent
⭐ Recommend the next best sales action
⭐ Allow opportunity updates through natural language
⭐ Retrieve the latest customer interaction
⭐ Automate deal approvals and email notifications
⭐ Maintain data security and controlled access
